{"tid":1983956,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"科大校方承認選舉結果 符佩瑩正式成為學生校董","createTime":"2020-04-22T06:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T05:34:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":126,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd74648f694505afd91c75f46a9dd7037db06ef","tid":1983956,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"【校方承認選舉結果 任命程序繼續進行】<br />\n<br />\n校方於今夜(21號)公布校董選舉重選的投訴處理進度，表示根據選舉規律第12.3條，選舉主任及學務長已經調查有關選舉的投訴，並裁定這次重選成立，結果有效。<br />\n<br />\n這意味著，因在政綱中加入「光復香港，時代革命」而擊敗曾四度落選、支持「校園去政治化」的內地學生學者聯誼會副主席盧普生而勝選的符佩瑩，將獲選舉主任提名至校董會作正式任命，成為學生校董。<br />\n<br />\n經過半年來的擾攘，符佩瑩的任期已經縮減至不足半年，但至少四個月前的「DQ」事件，不會重演。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkongstandstrong_live/16460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongstandstrong_live%2F16460&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8mSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=b6ef3375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkongstandstrong_live/16460</a>"},{"pid":"4cffd7050ac5cc29d680ad4d769df4e936b93a79","tid":1983956,"uid":68689,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"科大呢D垃圾學校不如執左佢啦"},{"pid":"278b1002c4ecffd6f602b2e15b3efbb73f69138d","tid":1983956,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T07:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e260d20b5289d2a97acb2421b6825500f6eae3d4","tid":1983956,"uid":253016,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T07:45:01.000Z","msg":"條北方胡種支那豬真係睇見都唔開胃"},{"pid":"cb5b222a1a2b45e7d7ca5592238c72bef36cd7ef","tid":1983956,"uid":2772,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"屌 支那學校冇撚用<br />\n拖得嗰兩日 最後咪又係要俾 垃圾"},{"pid":"e6db6b1b5a2a3401edc379fcaf55d4c8fe595833","tid":1983956,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 